quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  60,12,"Eehey ma annabi si rew…ďe juul…ďe ngari e ma ho…ďe coodandira e ma nde …ďe ndenndinta Alla e hay gooto,ngujjata njinata, mbarata sukaa…ďe mu' en,ngaddata fenaande fekindaande hakkunde juu…óe mu' en e koy…óe mum en,…ďe ngoopataa ma e mo∆ī∆īere ndeen de soodandir e mum 'en, yaafnano…ďe Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatoo…óo jurmotoo…óo"
  60,13,"Eehey mjon goooŇč…ói…ďe wote keetne yim…ďe …ďe Alla tikkani e dow mu'en, …ďe pi…ďtiima e La'akara hono no he'efer…ďe pi…ďtari e yim…ďe genaale."
  61,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo oon."
  61,2,"Eehey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe ko wa…ói ho…óon kaala ko on mba…óata."
  61,3,"Mawni tikkere ka Alla nde kaalaton ko on ngollata."
  61,4,"Pellet Alla na yi…ói …ďeen ha…ďatee…ďe e laawol Alla he…ďe ngoni saffeeji hono maadi fotndaandi."
  61,5,"Tumo nde o maakani yim…ďe makko, yim…ďe am holko taki ho…óon lora mi te ho…óon nganndi komi nelaa…óo Alla fa'ade e mon, nde…ďe oo√Īi Alla oo√Īi …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe Alla feewnata yim…ďe faasiqee…ďe."